{"tid":2205890,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"歐盟主席罕有回嗆習近平　表示將啟動人權制裁機制立法","createTime":"2020-09-17T06:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T12:13:12.000Z","uid":261647,"like":224,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"3f08ae68a68cb833c80ab3a1b72c31e368fa496f","tid":2205890,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:21:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gaus.ee/2020/09/soteu-von-der-leyen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgaus.ee%2F2020%2F09%2Fsoteu-von-der-leyen%2F&d=WBhgCLuhUD%2FUeH80S3I9%2BlgnvSLZGSqUYyTYHJNLWIM%3D&h=35371c67\" target=\"_blank\">https://gaus.ee/2020/09/soteu-von-der-leyen/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LNSdKoe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLNSdKoe.png&h=d26736ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n歐盟理事會主席馮黛蘭發表首份「歐情咨文」，一般預料唔會有大事發生，但罕有公然回嗆習近平。<br />\n<br />\n咨文提到，歐盟「一定會為香港同維吾爾人遭人權侵犯發聲」，並會就歐盟嘅馬格尼茲法案提交草案。<br />\n<br />\n而咨文當中一段，明顯是針對習近平在歐契「峰會」上嘅批評。馮黛蘭歐洲唔係無人權問題，例如「反猶太種族主義」，但歐洲可以討論，可以批評，甚至批評權利受到法律保障，明顯是回嗆中共總書記嘅「反擊」。<br />\n<br />\n但馮黛蘭嘅演說都仲有人唔收貨。比利時前首相伏思達都仲批評歐盟係香港問題，有聲明無實際，明顯要求對方加快制裁法案。"},{"pid":"4d7a024ef60c51bb734cffbd1e5bf4c819701930","tid":2205890,"uid":228868,"like":3,"dislike":8,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:23:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好嬲好嬲"},{"pid":"6791f9f7c2d5f1ddd2baa619018e4ef7a522cb6a","tid":2205890,"uid":228868,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支足"},{"pid":"c28d492887845fcd9f72e86ab0e8b07fc5fdfc03","tid":2205890,"uid":52705,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T06:25:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\"